examples.en: He hiked himself onto the top bunk.
I hiked myself onto the ledge.
The landlord hiked up the rents.
We hiked some of the shorter trails.
We hiked through a variety of terrains.
She hiked 10 miles in the hot desert sun.
They hiked out to a retired beach and fished in the surf.
They hiked through the flume and into the meadow beyond it.
